            <lg xml:id="TK1297">
<l>nāṇu maṟantē ṉavarmaṟak kallāveṉ</l>
<l>māṇā maṭaneñciṟ paṭṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have even forgotten my modesty, having been caught in my foolish mind which is not dignified enough to forget him.</l>
